{
  "texts": [
    "By injecting at only the final prompt token, the model must:1.",
    "Notice an anomaly at a specific moment in time 2.",
    "Retain that information across subsequent autoregressive steps Decode the semantic content of the transient signal into languageThe fact that our model succeeds at this task (85% accuracy on novel concepts at α = 40, with 95% detection rate) demonstrates that 7B models possess the attentional and memory capacity for genuine thought monitoring.",
    "The injected concept appears only once, at the boundary between prompt and generation, yet the model can detect its presence and identify its content with high reliability.",
    "Zero False Positives: Evidence for GroundingPerhaps the most striking result is the 0% false positive rate across all 60 control trials (95% CI: [0%-6%])."
